default function ProfileDetailsPage() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const { user } = useAuth(); const [error, setError] = useState(""); const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ name: "", type: "", mission_statement: "", core_values: [], target_audience: "", partnership_goals: [], location: { state: "", city: "", }, website: "", industry: "", }); const [selectedState, setSelectedState] = useState(""); useEffect(() => { const orgType = localStorage.getItem("orgType"); if (!orgType) { navigate("/profile-setup/type"); } else { setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, type: orgType, })); } }, [navigate]); const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); console.log("开始提交表单数据..."); try { // 验证核心价值观数量 if (formData.core_values.length > 3) { setError("核心价值观最多只能有3个"); return; } const token = localStorage.getItem("token"); console.log("准备发送的数据:", formData); const response = await fetch("http://localhost:3001/api/profile", { method: "POST", headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`, }, body: JSON.stringify(formData), }); const data = await response.json(); console.log("服务器响应:", data); if (!response.ok) { throw new Error(data.message || "Server error"); } if (data.code === 0) { console.log("组织资料保存成功"); navigate("/home"); } else { throw new Error(data.message || "Unknown error"); } } catch (error) { console.error("错误详情:", error); setError(error.message || "保存组织资料时出错"); } }; const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; if (name === "state") { setSelectedState(value); setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, location: { ...prev.location, state: value, }, })); } else if (name === "city") { setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, location: { ...prev.location, city: value, }, })); } else if (name === "core_values") { const values = value .split(",") .map((v) => v.trim()) .filter((v) => v); setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, core_values: values, })); } else if (name === "partnership_goals") { const goals = value .split(",") .map((v) => v.trim()) .filter((v) => v); setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, partnership_goals: goals, })); } else { setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value, })); } }; return (
